"{\"uid\": \"nbcbayarea.com-paris-2024-summer-olympics-gymnastics-judges-are-judging-gymnasts-even-before-the-competition-gold-medalist-says-3607132\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Even before the start of their competition routines,Olympic gymnastsare under the scrutinizing eyes of the judges -\\u00a0and any mistake, even in warm-ups, could count against them.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 176, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"These judges who are on the Olympic floor are also showing up to your training,\\\" five-time Olympic medalist and gymnast Nastia Liukin said.\", \"from\": 178, \"to\": 318, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 299, \"end\": 312, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nastia_Liukin\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Nastia Liukin\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nastia_Liukin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nastia_Liukin\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"They sit there and they memorize your routines, they actually put them down on paper.\\\"\", \"from\": 319, \"to\": 406, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Watch NBC Bay Area News free wherever you are  Liukin competed for Team USA at the 2008 Beijing Olympics, where she was crowned the individualall-aroundchampion.\", \"from\": 408, \"to\": 569, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 414, \"end\": 426, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/KNTV\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"NBC Bay Area\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/KNTV\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/KNTV\"}, {\"begin\": 414, \"end\": 426, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/KNTV\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"NBC Bay Area\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/KNTV\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/KNTV\"}, {\"begin\": 475, \"end\": 483, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\", \"score\": 0.9533905719560373, \"rank\": 0.04872931398823251, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The retired athlete said judges seem to project mistakes gymnasts make during training onto their actual competition performance, even if the move was executed flawlessly in the Olympics arena.\", \"from\": 570, \"to\": 763, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That's why it's so important to \\\"train as if you are competing,\\\" according to Liukin, who spoke with Dr. Michael Gervais on the podcast \\\"Finding Mastery.\\\"\", \"from\": 765, \"to\": 919, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 878, \"end\": 885, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ricky_Gervais\", \"score\": 0.9999996538541072, \"rank\": 3.4614598608396136e-07, \"text\": \"Gervais\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ricky_Gervais\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ricky_Gervais\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I remember talking about this and someone said, 'But that's not fair,'\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 921, \"to\": 1003, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"'How are they getting to judge you before the competition?'\\\"\", \"from\": 1004, \"to\": 1065, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"When you step foot into the competition, the Village, thearena, the training hall -\\u00a0it's game on,\\\" Liukin added.\", \"from\": 1067, \"to\": 1180, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's a competition every time that you step onto the floor.\\\"\", \"from\": 1181, \"to\": 1242, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Watch all the action from the Paris Olympic and Paralympic Games live on Peacock\", \"from\": 1246, \"to\": 1326, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1276, \"end\": 1281, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999942764494122, \"rank\": 5.723878192737045e-05, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}]}"